$lang['In mathematics and computer science, hexadecimal (also base 16, or hex) is a positional numeral system with a radix, or base, of 16. It uses sixteen distinct symbols, most often the symbols 0–9 to represent values zero to nine, and A, B, C, D, E, F (or alternatively a–f) to represent values ten to fifteen. For example, the hexadecimal number 2AF3 is equal, in decimal, to (2 × 163) + (10 × 162) + (15 × 161) + (3 × 160) , or 10,995.'] = 'Sa mhatamaitic agus ríomheolaíocht, is córas uimhriúil suímh é heicsidheachúil (bonn 16, nó heics) le radix, nó bonn, de 16. Úsáideann sé sé shiombail déag ar leith, is minic na siombailí 0–9 chun luachanna náid go naoi a léiriú, agus A, B, C, D, E, F (nó a–f) chun luachanna a léiriú ó dheich go cúig déag. Mar shampla, tá an uimhir heicsidheachúil 2AF3 comhionann, ina dheachúil, le (2 × 163) + (10 × 162) + (15 × 161) + (3 × 160), nó 10,995.';
$lang['Each hexadecimal digit represents four binary digits (bits) (also called a "nibble"), and the primary use of hexadecimal notation is as a human-friendly representation of binary coded values in computing and digital electronics. For example, byte values can range from 0 to 255 (decimal) but may be more conveniently represented as two hexadecimal digits in the range 00 through FF. Hexadecimal is also commonly used to represent computer memory addresses.'] = 'Seasann gach digit heicsidheachúil do cheithre dhigit dhénártha (giotán) (ar a dtugtar “nibble” freisin), agus is í an phríomhúsáid a bhaintear as nodaireacht heicsidheachúil mar léiriú atá neamhdhíobhálach don duine ar luachanna dénártha códaithe sa ríomhaireacht agus sa leictreonaic dhigiteach. Mar shampla, féadann luachanna beart a bheith idir 0 agus 255 (deachúil) ach is féidir iad a léiriú ar bhealach níos áisiúla mar dhá dhigit heicsidheacha sa raon 00 trí FF. Úsáidtear heicsidheachúlach freisin chun seoltaí cuimhne ríomhaire a léiriú.';
$lang['Hex is an abbreviation of Hexadecimal, which is based on a base -16 structure and is used for simplifying how instructions to computers are represented. This 16 symbols number system was developed as a means of inhibiting an 8-bit binary number, so data can be encoded into computers effortlessly. It can be imprinted and typed using two different hex digits with each hex digit demonstrating a nibble or perhaps a 4-bits format.'] = 'Is giorrúchán de Heicsidheachúlach é Heics, atá bunaithe ar bhunstruchtúr -16 agus a úsáidtear chun an chaoi a léirítear treoracha do ríomhairí a shimpliú. Forbraíodh an córas uimhreacha 16 siombail seo mar mhodh chun uimhir dhénártha 8-ghiotán a chosc, ionas gur féidir sonraí a ionchódú i ríomhairí gan stró. Is féidir é a phriontáil agus a chlóscríobh ag baint úsáide as dhá dhigit heicsidheachúlach éagsúla le gach digit heicsidheachúlach ag taispeáint nibble nó b&#39;fhéidir formáid 4-ghiotán.';
$lang['This number system uses 16 symbols that are represented in a range from 0-9 or A-F. The 0–9 represent numbers up to nine whereas A-F is represented by the numeric 10–15. As compared to the other three types of number systems, the hexadecimal numeral system is considered to be the most effective one.'] = 'Úsáideann an córas uimhreach seo 16 shiombail a léirítear i raon 0-9 nó AF. Seasann an 0–9 d’uimhreacha suas go dtí a naoi agus seasann AF leis an uimhriúil 10–15. I gcomparáid leis na trí chineál eile córas uimhreacha, meastar gurb é an córas uimhriúil heicsidheachúil an ceann is éifeachtaí.';
